{"tid":904209,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Sharp輸到癡撚左線#@_@#dog","createTime":"2018-11-16T07:11:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-17T18:23:40.000Z","uid":54481,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"593671d2899ac97bae4d1ffe352687ca2e24c483","tid":904209,"uid":54481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T07:11:57.000Z","msg":"Andy Yang 40 分鐘前<br />\nSharp 覺得螢幕挖兩個洞比一個更好<br />\n<img src=\"https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?resize=2000%2C2000%2Cshrink&amp;image_uri=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen-US%2Fhomerun%2Fengadget_479%2F16e52ffc9315e9b166584dd99e71ab38&amp;client=a1acac3e1b3290917d92&amp;signature=064d7bdbe79055b43755018c0f5fa388b4e78ef3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fo.aolcdn.com%2Fimages%2Fdims%3Fresize%3D2000%252C2000%252Cshrink%26image_uri%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fmedia.zenfs.com%252Fen-US%252Fhomerun%252Fengadget_479%252F16e52ffc9315e9b166584dd99e71ab38%26client%3Da1acac3e1b3290917d92%26signature%3D064d7bdbe79055b43755018c0f5fa388b4e78ef3&h=cd7abc23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這可不是軟體失控，而是利用 Android 的新異形屏規範的第一款產品囉。雖然目前手機的主流已經由瀏海又再次朝著縮小切割（水滴）、或是隱藏相機的解決方案前進，自己做面板的夏普顯然覺得這是個炫耀技術的好機會，發表了一台上下各切一個口的 Aquos R2 Compact。上面的小洞是挖給前鏡頭的，而下面的大洞呢？原來是指紋辨識器囉。<br />\n<br />\nAquos R2 Compact 雖然名為「Compact」，但 5.2 吋、2,280 x 1,080 解析度的 IGZO 面板放到前幾年也是標準大小。其他規格包括 Snapdragon 845 處理器、4GB 記憶體、22.6MP 主相機（單鏡）、和 64GB 儲存空間。做為小型的機種，2,500mAh 的電力也算是在意料之中，就不知道縮小的面板能不能多少幫忙加長一下使用時長了。<br />\n<br />\nR2 Compact 預計明年一月中在日本推出，至於其他市場就比較難說，但台灣應該還是有機會的。不過說真的，原本挖洞就是權宜之計，市面上這麼多瀏海手機是不得已，不是因為消費者喜歡面板被挖洞啊...<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FTsKJwcGXjw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DFTsKJwcGXjw&d=r63qQnKPzSXfNbk9McQvdaS6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=54b73682\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FTsKJwcGXjw</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chinese.engadget.com/2018/11/16/sharp-aquos-r2-compact-two-notches/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchinese.engadget.com%2F2018%2F11%2F16%2Fsharp-aquos-r2-compact-two-notches%2F&d=r63qQnKPzSXfNbk9McQvdaS6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=5a8cc150\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://chinese.engadget.com/2018/11/16/sharp-aquos-r2-compact-two-notches/</a><br />\n經由: Engadget<br />\n來源: Sharp"},{"pid":"b9d8e09c982b773311ad61dc66fe46906113bb55","tid":904209,"uid":54481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T07:22:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faa8115f14009b1ff70d5d38a8ccd35b533c1376","tid":904209,"uid":49664,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T07:32:19.000Z","msg":"利益關係  台積電和夏普伙伴關係<br />\n<br />\nsharp有個大財團在背後"},{"pid":"217010a854e8ee6371ddd7557f1c0795b0f0a3a1","tid":904209,"uid":25689,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T07:38:33.000Z","msg":"Sharp 個最大股東係郭台銘"},{"pid":"938fc21c25d8ca07459cbcfbe7d0fc2f8de9a6ea","tid":904209,"uid":12628,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T07:47:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VszGi5k.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVszGi5k.png&h=050f5f94&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1c7009fbc33b01f9d7dc6bf98873d7311c16d399","tid":904209,"uid":49664,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"217010a854e8ee6371ddd7557f1c0795b0f0a3a1","tid":904209,"uid":25689,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T07:38:33.000Z","msg":"Sharp 個最大股東係郭台銘"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T08:04:33.000Z","msg":"手機輸得幾多    有錢就任性"},{"pid":"f5513f2c79b5607fc589f2b8a8d7f47b89044ffc","tid":904209,"uid":57,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T05:11:27.000Z","msg":"其實葵興果棟sharp咁大棟係租俾人定唔係成棟都係sharp起?"},{"pid":"6a503c270a1e4d142d7b62ada58ff8a1f89f9020","tid":904209,"uid":25653,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T07:57:16.000Z","msg":"下一部 挖夠4個"},{"pid":"e9227